 {1 \over n} (f'(x) - \epsilon) < {1 \over n} (f'(x) + {r({1 \over n}) \over {1 \over n}}) <{1 \over n} (f'(x) + \epsilon) 
\left( 1+ {1 \over n}({ f'(x) - \epsilon \over f(x)}) \right)^n < \left( { f(x+{1 \over n}) \over f(x)}  \right)^n \le \left( 1+ {1 \over n}({ f'(x) + \epsilon \over f(x)})  \right)^n
